title: Osho's Place
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Western, Fast food, Salad bar, Beer/Wine, Take-out
description: Vegetarian food, smoothies, and a salad bar that's self-serve and priced by weight. Breakfast food til 11am, then salad bar and main dish and soup 12-10pm. Offers Sunday brunch. Free W-Lan. Its adjoined The Vegan Garden next door shut in 2015.
